Subject: [PATCH] Interfaces to use the sail-riscv v0.12 c_emulator as RVVTS
 DuT

Add support for memory dump and stop on breakpoint
for
sail-riscv c_emulator
commit 65ddde80ee2b131bf46c20e6e748343c336c4071 (tag: 0.12).

Signed-off-by: Manfred SCHLAEGL <manfred.schlaegl@gmx.at>
